{"id":"wqP7nSudZJpKVk2t","meta":{"instanceId":"8443f10082278c46aa5cf3acf8ff0f70061a2c58bce76efac814b16290845177","templateCredsSetupCompleted":true},"name":"Autonomous B2B Supplier Price Negotiation Agent","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"01763d50-3e91-49c2-b6e2-9008460542a3","name":"Sticky Note — Workflow Overview","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-3168,2928],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":560,"height":620,"content":"# 🤖 Autonomous B2B Supplier Price Negotiation Agent\n\n## Overview\nThis workflow autonomously negotiates supplier prices by generating AI-crafted emails, sending them, monitoring for replies, and logging all outcomes.\n\n## Workflow Stages\n1. **Trigger** — Polls Google Sheets every minute for new supplier rows\n2. **Validation** — Cleans and validates incoming row data\n3. **AI Draft Generation** — MCTS produces 3 negotiation angle drafts\n4. **Self-Critique** — 2-round LLM review refines the best draft\n5. **Email Dispatch** — Final email sent via Gmail with a unique REF ID\n6. **Reply Monitoring** — Waits 24h, then checks inbox for supplier reply\n7. **Outcome Routing** — Reply received → log + Slack; No reply → DPO retry\n8. **Logging** — Results written to Notion + Google Sheets\n\n## Owner\n**Automation Team — Techdome**\nEnvironment: Production\nLast Updated: June 2026"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"210c6ab6-da1a-45c6-8120-3b473651bb62","name":"Sticky Note — Trigger","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2512,2528],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":400,"height":524,"content":"# 📋 Trigger — New Supplier Row\n\nPolls **Sheet1** of the Negotiation Google Sheet every minute.\n\n## Important\n- Fires on **every row change**, not just new rows — idempotency is handled downstream via `Status` field checks\n- Uses a dedicated OAuth2 trigger credential separate from the write credential\n- `Row ID` must be populated in the sheet to ensure stable de-duplication\n\n## Sheet Columns Required\n`Supplier Name`, `Supplier URL`, `Supplier Email`, `Product / Item`, `Quantity`, `Our Budget ($)`, `Listed Price ($)`, `Status`"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"2d1e16b7-8bf5-4b78-9cee-b8f13f9bed05","name":"Sticky Note — Validation","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-2384,3392],"parameters":{"color":3,"width":400,"height":504,"content":"# 🔍 Input Validation & Data Preparation\n\nNormalises raw Google Sheets row data into a clean JSON payload for downstream nodes.\n\n## Key Operations\n- Converts Excel serial dates to ISO 8601 format\n- Strips Markdown mailto links from email fields (Sheets wraps hyperlinks)\n- Throws a hard error if any required field is missing — prevents partial executions\n\n## Warning\nIf `Listed Price ($)` is empty, it falls back to `Our Budget ($)` — savings calculations will show 0%. Ensure the sheet always contains a listed price for accurate reporting."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"6385d207-07de-4a68-a5a7-bf0533a0a0c0","name":"Sticky Note — MCTS Draft Generation","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1936,2400],"parameters":{"color":2,"width":460,"height":660,"content":"# 🧠 MCTS AI Draft Generation\n\nUses **Monte Carlo Tree Search (MCTS)** logic via GPT-4o-mini to generate 3 negotiation email drafts — each using a distinct persuasion angle.\n\n## Negotiation Angles\n- **BULK_DISCOUNT** — Leverage order volume for a price reduction\n- **COMPETITOR_MATCH** — Signal active vendor evaluation to pressure pricing\n- **LOYALTY_OFFER** — Offer long-term business commitment in exchange for a discount\n\n## Scoring Rubric (0–10)\n- Tone: 0–3\n- Specificity: 0–3\n- Persuasiveness: 0–4\n\n## LLM Notes\n- Model: `gpt-4o-mini`\n- Response must be pure JSON — no markdown fencing\n- Downstream parser will throw if JSON is malformed"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"dff39c12-fa12-42c1-837e-bf7266cd6e4b","name":"Sticky Note — Pick Best Draft","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1744,3280],"parameters":{"color":2,"width":380,"height":432,"content":"# 🏆 Pick Best Draft\n\nSorts the 3 MCTS-generated drafts by score (descending) and selects the top-ranked one for refinement.\n\n## Logic\n- All 3 drafts are preserved in `allDrafts` for use by the DPO retry path\n- The best draft's `angle`, `subject`, `message`, and `score` are promoted to top-level fields\n\n## Dependency\nReferences `Prepare & Validate Data` node — ensure node name matches exactly if renamed."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"1153aa7e-ef7f-412f-9269-500f7d4c5fbd","name":"Sticky Note — Self-Critique Rounds","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-1344,2432],"parameters":{"color":2,"width":460,"height":624,"content":"# 🔁 Self-Critique Pipeline (Rounds 1 & 2)\n\nTwo sequential LLM passes refine the selected draft before it is sent.\n\n## Round 1 — Refine Draft\nCritiques the best MCTS draft for tone, specificity, credibility, and clarity. Returns an improved version.\n\n## Round 2 — Final Polish (No-Reply Path)\nTriggered only when no supplier reply is received. Applies **DPO (Direct Preference Optimization)** logic — picks the next-best angle and rewrites with more urgency.\n\n## Notes\n- Both rounds use `gpt-4o-mini`\n- The critique text is stored and later written to the Notion audit log for QA review\n- Do not skip Round 1 — it is the gate between raw MCTS output and sent email"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"04c47fab-1890-4a80-8bc1-27f211b7ec3c","name":"Sticky Note — Email Dispatch","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-976,3264],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":420,"height":476,"content":"# 📧 Email Dispatch\n\nSends the final negotiation email to the supplier via Gmail.\n\n## Important\n- `[REF-{rowId}]` is appended to every subject line — this is how the reply-check filter identifies matching inbox threads\n- `replyTo` is set to `procurement@yourcompany.com` — update before going live\n- The `sendTo` field is currently hardcoded to `supplier@example.com` — **replace with `{{ $json.supplierEmail }}`** for production use\n\n## Warning\nDo not remove the `[REF-...]` subject tag. The Gmail reply-check node uses it as the inbox search query. Removing it will break reply detection."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"ed0a2c83-e5ae-4fcc-aaed-2b233518b9ac","name":"Sticky Note — Reply Monitoring","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-528,2464],"parameters":{"width":440,"height":572,"content":"# ⏳ Reply Monitoring Window\n\nAfter the initial email is sent, the workflow pauses for **24 hours** before checking the inbox.\n\n## How It Works\n1. `Mark Email Sent in Sheet` — logs `Status = Email Sent` immediately after dispatch\n2. `Wait 24 Hours` — suspends execution (uses n8n's built-in wait/resume mechanism)\n3. `Check Supplier Reply` — searches Gmail inbox for threads matching the `[REF-{rowId}]` subject tag\n\n## Warning\n- The Wait node uses a **webhook resume** — do not delete or disable it in production\n- n8n execution timeout must be set to **> 24 hours** in instance settings, or the wait will fail\n- Gmail search is limited to 5 results; this is sufficient since we search by unique REF ID"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d44054cc-fd88-436f-ac48-73469424220f","name":"Sticky Note — Reply Decision","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-208,3296],"parameters":{"width":440,"height":556,"content":"# ❓ Reply Decision Branch\n\nRoutes execution based on whether a supplier reply was detected in the inbox.\n\n## Branch A — Reply Received (True)\n→ `Process & Score Supplier Reply` → `Log in Notion` → `Update Google Sheets` → `Slack Alert (Complete)`\n\n## Branch B — No Reply (False)\n→ `Self-Critique Round 2 (DPO)` → `Build Retry Prompt` → `Send Follow-Up Email` → `Mark Retry in Sheet` → `Slack Retry Alert`\n\n## Note\nFinal price extraction in Branch A is currently a **placeholder** — the `savingsAmount` and `savingsPct` use the budget as the final price. Integrate an AI extraction step if real supplier price data is available in the reply."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"1acc0d62-9073-4257-8a5a-38e5a5757fc4","name":"Sticky Note — Outcome Logging","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[160,2272],"parameters":{"color":3,"width":440,"height":636,"content":"# 📒 Outcome Logging — Notion + Google Sheets\n\nAll negotiation results are logged for audit, reporting, and team review.\n\n## Notion Log\n- Creates a new page under the configured Notion database\n- Includes: supplier details, angle used, full email body, AI critique notes\n- Page URL is written back to Google Sheets for traceability\n\n## Google Sheets — Final Update\n- Writes: `Status`, `Final Price ($)`, `Savings %`, `Notion Log URL`\n- Uses Sheet1 for final status — ensure column names match exactly\n\n## Dependency\n- Notion credential: `Notion account -anuj`\n- Sheets credential: `Google Sheets account-anuj(td)`\n- Both must have write access before activating in production"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"9539b3dc-8f7d-478d-acb1-a84813a27869","name":"Sticky Note — Slack Notifications","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[880,2288],"parameters":{"width":440,"height":588,"content":"# 🔔 Slack Notifications\n\nTwo Slack alerts are fired depending on the negotiation outcome.\n\n## Alert 1 — Negotiation Complete\nSent to channel `C0B0QTA3KG9` when a supplier reply is detected.\nIncludes: listed price, final price, savings %, angle used, and Notion log link.\n\n## Alert 2 — Retry Sent\nSent when no reply is received after 24 hours. Includes the new angle and DPO strategy reasoning.\n\n## Warning\n- Both nodes use **Slack Webhook** authentication — rotate the webhook URL if it expires\n- Channel ID `C0B0QTA3KG9` is hardcoded — update if the procurement channel changes\n- Slack messages reference `$('Process Reply Data')` — ensure that node name is not renamed"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"d2ccee25-3d1b-42d7-a10d-5c1182a152d2","name":"Sticky Note — DPO Retry Path","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[576,3456],"parameters":{"color":6,"width":440,"height":572,"content":"# 🔄 DPO Retry Path\n\nWhen no supplier reply is received within 24 hours, this path fires a second, stronger email using a different negotiation angle.\n\n## DPO Logic\n- Selects the **next-best angle** from the original 3 MCTS drafts (not the one already sent)\n- Rewrites with: increased urgency, 48-hour response deadline, competitor hints, shorter body (<120 words)\n\n## Tracking\n- `Angle Tried` column in the sheet is updated to the retry angle for analytics\n- `Retry Sent At` timestamp is recorded for SLA tracking\n\n## Warning\nThis workflow does **not** send a third follow-up. If the retry also receives no reply, manual intervention is required. Consider linking to a escalation sub-workflow here."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"3169c412-7ce0-4517-a3bf-b500da7ae340","name":"📋 Trigger — New Supplier Row1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheetsTrigger","position":[-2304,3088],"parameters":{"options":{},"pollTimes":{"item":[{"mode":"everyMinute"}]},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gid=0","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk/edit#gid=0","cachedResultName":"Sheet1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"Negotiation sheet"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsTriggerOAuth2Api":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Google Sheets Trigger account 2"}},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"89b076f4-d30d-4e6c-bfca-fb238ed2bbca","name":"🔍 Validate & Prepare Supplier Data1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-2096,3088],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const row = $input.first().json;\n\n// Helper to convert Excel serial date to ISO string\nfunction excelDateToISO(serial) {\n  if (!serial || isNaN(serial)) return '';\n  const date = new Date((serial - 25569) * 86400 * 1000);\n  return date.toISOString();\n}\n\n// Clean email — strip markdown link format [email](mailto:email)\nfunction cleanEmail(val) {\n  if (!val) return '';\n  const match = val.match(/\\[([^\\]]+)\\]\\(mailto:[^\\)]+\\)/);\n  return match ? match[1] : val;\n}\n\n// Validate required fields (using ACTUAL column names from your sheet)\nif (!row['Supplier URL'] || !row['Product / Item'] || !row['Quantity'] || !row['Our Budget ($)']) {\n  throw new Error('Missing required fields: Supplier URL, Product / Item, Quantity, or Our Budget ($)');\n}\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    rowId:        row['Row ID'] || Date.now().toString(),\n    supplierName: row['Supplier Name'] || 'Unknown Supplier',\n    supplierUrl:  row['Supplier URL'],\n    supplierEmail: cleanEmail(row['Supplier Email']),\n    product:      row['Product / Item'],\n    quantity:     row['Quantity'],\n    budget:       row['Our Budget ($)'],\n    listedPrice:  row['Listed Price ($)'] || row['Our Budget ($)'],\n    requestDate:  excelDateToISO(row['Request Date']),\n    messageSentAt: excelDateToISO(row['Message Sent At']),\n    retrySentAt:  excelDateToISO(row['Retry Sent At']),\n    finalPrice:   row['Final Price ($)'] || null,\n    status:       row['Status'] || 'Pending',\n    angleTried:   row['Angle Tried'] || '',\n    timestamp:    new Date().toISOString()\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"07bf2587-6267-41c8-8480-0f99f76b08bd","name":"🏆 Pick Best Draft1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-1456,3088],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const responseBody = $input.first().json;\nconst rawText = responseBody.content[0].text;\n\nlet drafts;\ntry {\n  drafts = JSON.parse(rawText);\n} catch (e) {\n  // Try to extract JSON from response if wrapped in text\n  const match = rawText.match(/\\[\\s*\\{[\\s\\S]*\\}\\s*\\]/);\n  if (match) {\n    drafts = JSON.parse(match[0]);\n  } else {\n    throw new Error('Could not parse MCTS drafts: ' + rawText);\n  }\n}\n\n// Sort by score descending\ndrafts.sort((a, b) => b.score - a.score);\n\nconst best = drafts[0];\nconst prevData = $('Prepare & Validate Data').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...prevData,\n    allDrafts: drafts,\n    bestDraft: best,\n    bestAngle: best.angle,\n    bestSubject: best.subject,\n    bestMessage: best.message,\n    bestScore: best.score\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"d57fddd2-2ad8-4dfb-9eef-a952579fc882","name":"📝 Parse Final Critique Output1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[-848,3088],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const responseBody = $input.first().json;\nconst rawText = responseBody.content[0].text;\n\nlet critique;\ntry {\n  critique = JSON.parse(rawText);\n} catch (e) {\n  const match = rawText.match(/\\{[\\s\\S]*\\}/);\n  if (match) {\n    critique = JSON.parse(match[0]);\n  } else {\n    throw new Error('Could not parse self-critique response: ' + rawText);\n  }\n}\n\nconst prevData = $('Pick Best Draft').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...prevData,\n    critique: critique.critique,\n    changesMade: critique.changes_made,\n    finalSubject: critique.final_subject,\n    finalMessage: critique.final_message\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"4ae7de60-9518-42de-9df5-a035fff3c453","name":"📧 Send Negotiation Email to Supplier1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[-624,3088],"webhookId":"d9a5e810-6313-4659-82fb-b315bc147c54","parameters":{"sendTo":"user@example.com","message":"={{ $json.finalMessage }}","options":{"replyTo":"user@example.com"},"subject":"={{ $json.finalSubject }} [REF-{{ $json.rowId }}]","emailType":"text"},"credentials":{"gmailOAuth2":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Gmail account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"b805f6b5-213e-4906-8f5d-ece488856a30","name":"✅ Mark Email Sent in Sheet1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[-400,3088],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{},"schema":[],"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","matchingColumns":[],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":false},"options":{},"operation":"update","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":1085802152,"cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk/edit#gid=1085802152","cachedResultName":"Sheet2"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"Negotiation sheet"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Google Sheets account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"3754c1a6-dbca-4d32-9f48-198cdbf24f32","name":"⏳ Wait 24 Hours for Reply1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.wait","position":[-176,3088],"webhookId":"wait-24h-supplier-negotiation","parameters":{"unit":"hours","amount":24},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"0fd6162c-797e-4217-a16a-65f072fb1584","name":"📬 Check Supplier Reply (Gmail)1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[32,3088],"webhookId":"1d2915c0-5e56-46a0-8199-0441d65b3103","parameters":{"limit":5,"filters":{"q":"=subject:[REF-{{ $('Parse Critique Result').first().json.rowId }}] in:inbox"},"operation":"getAll"},"credentials":{"gmailOAuth2":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Gmail account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"4a2aa892-1dc2-4709-9ee6-31033df986bd","name":"❓ Reply Received?1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.if","position":[256,3088],"parameters":{"options":{},"conditions":{"options":{"leftValue":"","caseSensitive":false,"typeValidation":"strict"},"combinator":"and","conditions":[{"id":"check_reply_condition","operator":{"type":"number","operation":"gt"},"leftValue":"={{ $json.messages ? $json.messages.length : 0 }}","rightValue":0}]}},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"b3b46d7c-0bb1-4899-bd6d-8fa293f54008","name":"🔄 Build DPO Retry Prompt1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[736,3248],"parameters":{"jsCode":"const responseBody = $input.first().json;\nconst rawText = responseBody.content[0].text;\n\nlet retry;\ntry {\n  retry = JSON.parse(rawText);\n} catch (e) {\n  const match = rawText.match(/\\{[\\s\\S]*\\}/);\n  if (match) {\n    retry = JSON.parse(match[0]);\n  } else {\n    throw new Error('Could not parse DPO retry: ' + rawText);\n  }\n}\n\nconst prevData = $('Parse Critique Result').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...prevData,\n    retryAngle: retry.angle_used,\n    retrySubject: retry.subject,\n    retryMessage: retry.message,\n    retryReasoning: retry.strategy_reasoning\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"1ae0afb2-bfb2-46cd-8aaa-045563cffabf","name":"📧 Send Follow-Up Retry Email1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.gmail","position":[928,3248],"webhookId":"b0a9eb35-89c0-47cd-9b22-b88183b5f67e","parameters":{"sendTo":"user@example.com","message":"={{ $json.retryMessage }}","options":{"replyTo":"user@example.com"},"subject":"={{ $json.retrySubject }} [REF-{{ $json.rowId }}]","emailType":"text"},"credentials":{"gmailOAuth2":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Gmail account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":2.1},{"id":"19b228cf-ce0d-42ce-b9ed-66af27307550","name":"✅ Mark Retry Sent in Sheet1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[1152,3248],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Status":"Retry Sent","Angle Tried":"={{ $json.retryAngle }}","Retry Sent At":"={{ new Date().toISOString() }}"},"mappingMode":"defineBelow"},"options":{},"operation":"update","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Sheet1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Google Sheets account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"ab9d62ad-d4bb-4710-b2a2-d50aa2dc9389","name":"⚙️ Process & Score Supplier Reply1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","position":[480,2944],"parameters":{"jsCode":"// This node handles REPLY RECEIVED path\n// Parse the email reply and extract negotiated price if mentioned\nconst replyData = $input.first().json;\nconst prevData = $('Parse Critique Result').first().json;\n\nconst replySnippet = replyData.messages && replyData.messages[0] ? replyData.messages[0].snippet : 'Reply received';\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...prevData,\n    outcome: 'Reply Received',\n    replySnippet: replySnippet,\n    finalStatus: 'Negotiated',\n    // Savings to be manually or AI-extracted — placeholder here\n    finalPrice: prevData.budget,\n    listedPrice: prevData.listedPrice,\n    savingsAmount: prevData.listedPrice - prevData.budget,\n    savingsPct: (((prevData.listedPrice - prevData.budget) / prevData.listedPrice) * 100).toFixed(2)\n  }\n}];"},"typeVersion":2},{"id":"f25122a0-4c6e-4896-86a2-e57d0c7b660c","name":"📒 Log Negotiation Result in Notion1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.notion","position":[704,2944],"parameters":{"title":"=Negotiation — {{ $json.supplierName }} — {{ $json.product }} — {{ new Date().toLocaleDateString() }}","pageId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"url","value":"https://www.notion.so/Test-n8n-automation-350f839f118480fb9bddfb4278f2ae4e"},"blockUi":{"blockValues":[{"type":"heading_2","textContent":"Negotiation Summary"},{"textContent":"=Supplier: {{ $json.supplierName }} | Product: {{ $json.product }} | Qty: {{ $json.quantity }}"},{"type":"heading_3","textContent":"Messages Sent"},{"textContent":"=ANGLE 1 ({{ $json.bestAngle }} | Score: {{ $json.bestScore }})\n\nSubject: {{ $json.finalSubject }}\n\n{{ $json.finalMessage }}"},{"type":"heading_3","textContent":"Self-Critique Notes"},{"textContent":"={{ $json.critique }}"}]},"options":{}},"credentials":{"notionApi":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Notion account -anuj"}},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"973b6dfd-a18b-41f2-ae07-eb10b4df736c","name":"📊 Final Update in Google Sheets1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[928,2944],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"Status":"={{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.finalStatus || 'Completed' }}","Savings %":"={{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.savingsPct }}","Final Price":"={{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.finalPrice }}","Notion Log URL":"={{ $json.url }}"},"mappingMode":"defineBelow"},"options":{},"operation":"update","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"Sheet1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1AqoI7azDDBPYyV4cZmEAQkG7cL48bvvyIU5ti_Llebk/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"Negotiation sheet"}},"credentials":{"googleSheetsOAuth2Api":{"id":"credential-id","name":"Google Sheets account-anuj(td)"}},"typeVersion":4.5},{"id":"fcaaafee-7b5f-4d95-aa84-d9425d82b213","name":"🔔 Slack — Alert Procurement Team1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","position":[1152,2944],"webhookId":"948c5add-ca82-41ae-8046-f2a19c358c20","parameters":{"text":"=:white_check_mark: *Negotiation Complete*\n\n*Supplier:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.supplierName }}\n*Product:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.product }}\n*Quantity:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.quantity }} units\n\n:moneybag: *Listed Price:* ${{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.listedPrice }}\n:chart_with_downwards_trend: *Final Price:* ${{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.finalPrice }}\n:tada: *Savings:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.savingsPct }}%\n\n*Angle Used:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.bestAngle }}\n*Status:* {{ $('Process Reply Data').first().json.finalStatus }}\n\n:memo: Full audit log in Notion → {{ $('Notion — Log Negotiation').first().json.url }}","select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"C0B0QTA3KG9"},"otherOptions":{},"authentication":"webhook"},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"a98481ec-79b0-4c59-9f9e-1ecc544b47b4","name":"🔔 Slack — Retry Alert to Team1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","position":[1360,3248],"webhookId":"a4392d24-566b-40b5-87d5-272a3b3ec5f0","parameters":{"text":"=:warning: *No Reply — Retry Sent*\n\n*Supplier:* {{ $json.supplierName }}\n*Product:* {{ $json.product }}\n*Original Angle:* {{ $json.bestAngle }}\n*Retry Angle:* {{ $json.retryAngle }}\n*Strategy:* {{ $json.retryReasoning }}\n\nRetry email sent. Monitor for response.","select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"id","value":"C0B0QTA3KG9"},"otherOptions":{},"authentication":"webhook"},"typeVersion":2.2},{"id":"d499ca66-f92d-44f2-a07f-5f226516bbbd","name":"⚡ LLM — Draft Generator (GPT-4o)1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","position":[-2032,3296],"parameters":{"model":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"builtInTools":{}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"credential-id","name":"OpenAi account-TD"}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"6d1eb433-8d26-4e90-a5fa-e1cd86bd5665","name":"🧠 MCTS — Generate 3 Negotiation Drafts1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[-1856,3088],"parameters":{"text":"={{ JSON.stringify([{ role: 'user', content: `You are a professional B2B procurement negotiation expert. Generate exactly 3 negotiation email drafts for the following purchase request and score each one from 0–10.\n\nSupplier: ${$json.supplierName}\nProduct: ${$json.product}\nQuantity: ${$json.quantity} units\nOur Budget: $${$json.budget}\nListed Price: $${$json.listedPrice}\n\nGenerate 3 negotiation angles:\n1. BULK_DISCOUNT - Leverage quantity for a volume discount\n2. COMPETITOR_MATCH - Mention we are evaluating competitors and request price matching\n3. LOYALTY_OFFER - Offer long-term partnership/repeat business in exchange for better price\n\nFor each draft, write a professional, concise email (150–200 words). Score each on: tone (0-3), specificity (0-3), persuasiveness (0-4).\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON in this exact format, no markdown:\n[\n  {\n    \"angle\": \"BULK_DISCOUNT\",\n    \"subject\": \"email subject line\",\n    \"message\": \"full email body\",\n    \"score\": 8.5,\n    \"reasoning\": \"why this angle scores this way\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"angle\": \"COMPETITOR_MATCH\",\n    \"subject\": \"email subject line\",\n    \"message\": \"full email body\",\n    \"score\": 7.0,\n    \"reasoning\": \"why this angle scores this way\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"angle\": \"LOYALTY_OFFER\",\n    \"subject\": \"email subject line\",\n    \"message\": \"full email body\",\n    \"score\": 6.5,\n    \"reasoning\": \"why this angle scores this way\"\n  }\n]` }]) }}","options":{},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"1299d738-4802-46d6-a5be-b20d9b7e4f3f","name":"⚡ LLM — Critique Model (GPT-4o)1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","position":[-1360,3312],"parameters":{"model":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"builtInTools":{}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"credential-id","name":"OpenAi account-TD"}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"93153c74-664e-4c36-a5e4-f79b560db8dc","name":"🔁 Self-Critique Round 1 — Refine Draft1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[-1232,3088],"parameters":{"text":"={{ JSON.stringify([{ role: 'user', content: `You are a senior procurement communication expert performing a self-critique review.\n\nReview the following negotiation email draft and improve it if needed. Focus on:\n1. TONE: Professional, confident but not aggressive\n2. SPECIFICITY: Includes product name, quantity, specific ask\n3. CREDIBILITY: Sounds like a real business with genuine intent\n4. CLARITY: Clear call to action\n\nOriginal Draft:\nSubject: ${$json.bestSubject}\n\n${$json.bestMessage}\n\nProvide your critique and the FINAL IMPROVED VERSION. Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown:\n{\n  \"critique\": \"your brief critique (2-3 sentences)\",\n  \"changes_made\": \"what you changed and why\",\n  \"final_subject\": \"final subject line\",\n  \"final_message\": \"final email body ready to send\"\n}` }]) }}","options":{},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"b7526cea-ac3c-4365-9098-3b1a14095779","name":"⚡ LLM — Final Polish Model (GPT-4o)1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenAi","position":[336,3408],"parameters":{"model":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gpt-4o-mini","cachedResultName":"gpt-4o-mini"},"options":{},"builtInTools":{}},"credentials":{"openAiApi":{"id":"credential-id","name":"OpenAi account-TD"}},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"40696c6a-57ee-42d1-889f-c6fec8b20fcd","name":"🔁 Self-Critique Round 2 — Final Polish1","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[432,3248],"parameters":{"text":"={{ JSON.stringify([{ role: 'user', content: `You are a procurement negotiation expert. The first email was sent but received no reply within 24 hours. Apply DPO (Direct Preference Optimization) logic to craft a stronger follow-up.\n\nContext:\n- Supplier: ${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.supplierName}\n- Product: ${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.product}\n- Quantity: ${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.quantity}\n- Budget: $${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.budget}\n- First angle tried: ${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.bestAngle}\n- First message score: ${$('Parse Critique Result').first().json.bestScore}\n- All drafted angles: ${JSON.stringify($('Parse Critique Result').first().json.allDrafts.map(d => d.angle))}\n\nThe supplier ignored our first email. Now pick the NEXT BEST angle from the remaining drafts and rewrite it to be:\n1. More assertive and urgent\n2. Mention that we need a response within 48 hours\n3. Hint at competitor alternatives\n4. Shorter and punchier (under 120 words)\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON:\n{\n  \"angle_used\": \"angle name\",\n  \"subject\": \"follow-up subject line\",\n  \"message\": \"follow-up email body\",\n  \"strategy_reasoning\": \"why this approach works better now\"\n}` }]) }}","options":{},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":3.1}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"9775f3fb-79e6-4f95-a834-93ad1c37a437","connections":{"❓ Reply Received?1":{"main":[[{"node":"⚙️ Process & Score Supplier Reply1","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"🔁 Self-Critique Round 2 — Final Polish1","type":"main","index":0}]]},"🏆 Pick Best Draft1":{"main":[[{"node":"🔁 Self-Critique Round 1 — Refine Draft1","type":"main","index":0}]]},"⏳ Wait 24 Hours for Reply1":{"main":[[{"node":"📬 Check Supplier Re